WSO2 ESB is a production grade open source ESB solution based on the lightweight Apache Synapse ESB with highest performance, lowest footprint, and most interoperable SOA and integration middl eware today.
Relying on our innovative Carbon technology, the ESB delivers a smooth start-to-finish project experience that you cannot find anywhere else. 
The feature rich and standards compliant WSO2 ESB delivers high performance within a lean footprint.
For example, a deployed WSO2 ESB often fits within a 160 MB memory space. 
WSO2 ESB supports service mediation, message mediation, load balancing, clustering and many more enterprise integration techniques. 
It also supports a range of application and transport level protocols such as HTTP, JMS, Mail, VFS and FIX.